Build Instructions (may require tweaking)
**jdk 1.7 and ant must be installed to build the easy way**
1. Clone the repo into an empty folder named Daemon.
2. Download mcp72.zip and minecraft forge 4.0.0.234.zip from their respective sites, and copy them into Daemon/downloads.
3. Start a shell in the main folder and run "ant install package".
4. Find the compiled jar in Daemon.

